         <abstract id="aspace_3790291acf742a83337879b52f4020e1">Gift of Lydia Tunnard (Mrs. Christopher Tunnard), from the estate of her brother. Miscellaneous collection of mounted black and white photographs, mostly Alinari photographs of well-known monuments. Some material periodically removed from this collection and filed with general collection. Many photographs are faded.</abstract>
